# MARLIN — local env stub
#
# The repo-level .env (../.env) is the source of truth for LLM provider config.
# Copy ../.env.example to ../.env and fill in ONE provider's vars (Kamiwaza,
# OpenAI, OpenRouter, Anthropic, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint).
#
# See ../DEPLOY.md for the full provider table.
#
# Anything you set here overrides the repo-level .env for this app only.
# Common per-app overrides:
#
# LLM_PRIMARY_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# LLM_FALLBACK_MODELS=gpt-4o-mini,gpt-4o
